  <td>subtle</td>
  <td>An additional <code>-subtle</code> class can be applied to remove the solid background color and provide a 1px border. For example, <code>sage-label-subtle</code> sets the text color, border color, and also sets the background color to white. Should also be used in tandem with the <code>type</code> to set the different color palettes.</td>
